{"tid":1952464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"20200331 世衛再次呼籲一般人不用戴口罩","createTime":"2020-03-31T15:22:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-01T04:45:02.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d007280c117fc1ecfe1c2ee9831da4b5be488588","tid":1952464,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T15:22:26.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情蔓延至全球，惟世衛曾建議民眾如沒有生病，不需要戴口罩。世衛生緊急項目執行總監 Mike Ryan 再次呼籲一般民眾，如非生病或照顧病人，不要戴口罩，指沒有證據顯示戴口罩有任何好處，反指戴錯會有反效果。<br />\n據CNN&nbsp;報道指，Mike Ryan 昨日（30日）於日內瓦的記者會上表示，沒有具體證據顯示戴口罩有任何潛在好處，戴錯反而會有反效果。他又指全球口罩和其他醫療用品也短缺，現時被病毒感染風險最高的是前線醫護人員，他們每日、每秒也會接觸病毒。<br />\n世衛傳染病流行病學家 Maria Van Kerkhove 亦指，應將口罩留給最有需要的人，重申不建議大眾在社區戴口罩，只建議生病或要照顧患者的人戴。"},{"pid":"92cec088317e6ec1bce2ea08830a307fd49ccd97","tid":1952464,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T15:23:20.000Z","msg":"譴責中國之前迫人戴口罩未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e48b084a0eba6f04642f6e8314455ef52ae6f92","tid":1952464,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T15:24:41.000Z","msg":"呢班友係咪想多啲人中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後再歌頌雜種"},{"pid":"9253530d57eac8c178d8fa778f7c624a53a4333c","tid":1952464,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T15:26:07.000Z","msg":"而家全球大爆發都叫人唔好戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世界人口死幾百萬不是夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79dfa3bdcfc817380b63a4a9fd8d8c10afb3c256","tid":1952464,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T15:26:38.000Z","msg":"We're S.P.E.C.I.A.L. People.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08010843edb5c4317b6464ee383d430b5eef0950","tid":1952464,"uid":320902,"like"